'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3238] on 9 January 2001 at 7:01:18 am'!"Change Set:		hibernateFlapsDate:			9 January 2001Author:			Bob ArningTo save space when publishing projects, hibernate the viewer flaps. Be sure to unhibernate when loading"!!PasteUpMorph methodsFor: 'flaps' stamp: 'RAA 1/9/2001 06:59'!releaseViewers	"In preparation for saving, make the flapTabs release their viewers."	self flapTabs do: [:ft | 		(ft respondsTo: #hibernate) ifTrue: [ft hibernate]]! !!ViewerFlapTab methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 1/9/2001 06:56'!unhibernate	"recreate my viewer"	referent ifNotNil: [		(referent findA: Viewer) ifNotNil: [^self].	].	^ self presenter viewMorph: scriptedPlayer costume! !